long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Introducing QuipDad, the ultimate tool for injecting a dose of dad humor into your everyday browsing experience! This whimsical extension is designed to bring laughter and groans to your digital adventures, offering a continuous stream of groan-inducing jokes right at your fingertips.

With the QuipDad Extension installed, you'll never be far from a pun-tastic punchline. Whether you're browsing the web, checking your emails, or simply scrolling through social media, this delightful extension will seamlessly integrate into your browser and surprise you with its witty one-liners and clever quips.
